01:58:21.137 --> 01:58:22.597
What is he saying?

784
01:58:25.308 --> 01:58:26.892
He says he loves us.

785
01:58:32.607 --> 01:58:33.983
We love you. Dad.

786
01:58:50.124 --> 01:58:52.001
No. let her go. It's her turn.

787
01:59:19.028 --> 01:59:19.862
Hello?

788
01:59:20.946 --> 01:59:22.031
<i>It's me.</i>

789
01:59:23.532 --> 01:59:25.284
It's late for you.

790
01:59:25.368 --> 01:59:27.203
<i>I don't really sleep.</i>

791
01:59:30.414 --> 01:59:31.582
Me neither.

792
01:59:33.793 --> 01:59:36.253
<i>I need to talk to you
about Charlie.</i>

793
01:59:39.715 --> 01:59:41.175
I'm listening.

794
02:01:36.499 --> 02:01:38.209
You know my face.

795
02:01:44.131 --> 02:01:46.342
You remember my Katie. don't you?

796
02:01:51.847 --> 02:01:54.683
She wants to know
if you'd like to see a trick.

